            <head xml:id="yyy8Uu-xd9180-Hd1e103">Caput 16</head>
            <p xml:id="yyy8Uu-xd9180-d1e106">
               <lb ed="#H" n="102"/>CAPUT XVI 
      <lb ed="#H" n="103"/>In quo de charitate erga posteros 
   mor<lb ed="#H" n="104" break="no"/>tuorum. 
    </p>
            <p xml:id="yyy8Uu-xd9180-d1e115">
               <lb ed="#H" n="105"/>CHARITAS erga posteros &amp; propinquos mortuorum, est quum 
      <lb ed="#H" n="106"/>ob charitatem quam complexi fuimus viventes &amp; retinemu. 
      <lb ed="#H" n="107"/>erga mortuos, benevolentiam &amp; officia utilia ac necessara 
      ex<lb ed="#H" n="108" break="no"/>hibemus etiam posteris &amp; propinquis illorum superstitibus. Ea enim 
      <lb ed="#H" n="109"/>est verae charitatis natura, ut morte ejus quem diligimus non 
      ab<lb ed="#H" n="110" break="no"/>rumpatur, sed veluti haereditatio jure ad posteros &amp; propinquosejus 
      <lb ed="#H" n="111"/>continuetur.  
    </p>
            <p xml:id="yyy8Uu-xd9180-d1e133">
               <lb ed="#H" n="112"/>
               <pc type="indent"/>Ita David declaravit charitatem suam erga Jonathanem, post 
      <lb ed="#H" n="113"/>mortem ejus benefaciendo Mephiboscheto filio Jonathanis. Sic 
      fi<lb ed="#H" n="114" break="no"/>deles ob amorem in defunctum, convivia exhibebant, vel cibos 
      mit<lb ed="#H" n="115" break="no"/>tebant posteris defuncti ad eos consolandos, Jerem. 16. 7. Ezech. 24. 
      <lb ed="#H" n="116"/>17. Tobi. 4. 18. Nam qui mortuorum necessariis benefacit, mortuis 
      <lb ed="#H" n="117"/>ipsis dicitur benefacere 
    </p>
